description: Demolition of the existing buildings occupying the site and redevelopment to provide five buildings of between four and ten storeys in height accommodating 2,687sqm retail floorspace and 208 residential units (comprising 2 x studio, 81 x 1 bed; 76 x 2 bed; 39 x 3 bed; 4 x 4 bed; 6 x 5 bed), 104 parking spaces and landscaped, public, communal and private amenity space.
